.env
**/__pycache__
**/node_modules
**/dist
*.log

# Local daemon runtime state (state.json, sysprompt.txt, disclaw.sock,
# missed-pings.log) when the daemon's started from a project-root cwd
# with the default DISCLAW_RUNTIME_DIR. Test runs with their own
# DISCLAW_RUNTIME_DIR (e.g. dev-test.sh's scratch dir) live elsewhere.
.disclaw/

# Agent-written artifacts that may land in cwd (e.g. feedback.md from
# a testing instance writing per welcome.testing.md). Track manually
# if a particular one is worth preserving.
feedback.md
